 Neovim  (leader = Space)

 Navigation
  Ctrl+D / Ctrl+U          page down/up (centered)
  n / N                    next/prev search (centered)
  Space+pv                 file explorer (Ex)
  Space+e                  toggle neotree

 Telescope
  Space+pf                 find files
  Ctrl+P                   find git files
  Space+ps                 grep search
  Space+fm                 find media
  Space+?                  search keymaps

 Harpoon
  Space+a                  mark file
  Ctrl+E                   open menu
  Ctrl+H/J/K/L             goto mark 1/2/3/4
  Ctrl+Shift+P/N           prev/next mark

 Git
  Space+gs                 fugitive
  Space+gg                 lazygit
  Space+gf                 lazygit current file
  Space+gc                 lazygit commits

 LSP
  gd                       goto definition
  gr                       goto references
  gI                       goto implementation
  gD                       goto declaration
  K                        hover docs
  Space+D                  goto type definition
  Space+rn                 rename
  Space+ca                 code action
  Space+ds                 document symbols
  Space+ws                 workspace symbols

 Debug (DAP)
  F5                       continue
  Shift+F5                 stop
  Ctrl+F5                  restart
  F10                      step over
  F11                      step into
  Shift+F11                step out
  Space+db                 toggle breakpoint
  Space+dB                 conditional breakpoint
  Space+du                 toggle debug UI
  Space+de                 evaluate expression
  Space+dC                 run to cursor

 CMake
  Space+cg                 generate
  Space+cb                 build
  Space+cr                 run
  Space+cd                 debug
  Space+cy                 select build type
  Space+ct                 select target

 Find & Replace (Spectre)
  Space+S                  toggle spectre
  Space+sw                 search word
  Space+sp                 search in file

 Editing
  V+J / V+K               move line down/up
  Space+y                  yank to clipboard
  Space+Y                  yank line to clipboard
  Space+u                  undo tree

 Tasks (Overseer)
  Space+ot                 toggle runner
  Space+or                 run task
  Space+ob                 build task

 Other
  Space+oo                 open related file
  Space+cp                 color picker
